desmarais llp  john m desmarais home  lawyers john m desmarais partner phone  fax  email vcard pdf jdesmaraisdesmaraisllpcom biography representative matters publications events john desmarais is the founding partner of desmarais llp  after practicing in the area of intellectual property litigation and counseling for several years at fish  neave in  he left private practice to serve as an assistant united states attorney in the southern district of new york where for three years he tried criminal jury trials for the federal government after leaving the government mr desmarais returned to fish  neave and to the practice of intellectual property litigation  in  he joined the new york office of kirkland  ellis as a partner from  he served as a member of kirklands firm management committee  after  years at kirkland in  mr desmarais left to found desmarais llp an intellectual property trial boutique that specializes in jury trials and alternative fee structures  mr desmaraiss  billion win for alcatellucent against microsoft resulted in one of the largest plaintiffs jury verdicts in a patent infringement action this win has been profiled in the following articles “microsoft hit with  billion verdict in mp suit” the wall street journal “mp patents in upheaval after verdict” the new york times “microsoft loses music patent case” the los angeles times and microsoft loses big in mp patent suit the washington post practice makes perfect for these hot litigators in the national law journal and bb takes on a whole new meaning in the national law journal additionally mr desmarais was quoted in this verdict made jaws drop in the national law journals profile of the top  verdicts of  mr desmarais was quoted in the road less traveled in the america lawyers “taming texas” cover story which referred to his two recent defense jury verdicts in the eastern district of texas marshall and sherman mr desmarais was quoted regarding the charter communications jury trial victory in “for a litigator on a streak theres a science to winning” the wall street journal mr desmarais was quoted in “what now for the usptos rules on continuations” in managing intellectual property dec jan  reporting on his success in obtaining an injunction against the ptos proposed new patent rules mr desmaraiss win for infineon technologies ag was featured in “same facts  different stories” from the march  edition of the american lawyer his success was also profiled in fortune “a hot stocks dirty secret” vol  no  pg  july   that article quotes some of mr desmaraiss key crossexamination and concludes that “during the trial rambus lawyers were outmaneuvered at every turn by a team from the new york office of kirkland  ellis” additionally mr desmarais was quoted regarding the rambus case in the following articles “a fatal paper cut ends rambuss case” the american lawyer “claim against infineon tossed” richmond timesdispatch “rambus is ordered by jury to pay  million to infineon over patents” the wall street journal and “californiabased chip designer rambus found guilty of fraud in patent case” san jose mercury news this case was also featured in the monthly “deals  suits” column in corporate counsel mr desmaraiss work on behalf of verizon wireless and several other cellular service providers was selected as defense verdict of the week by the national law journal the article is entitled “company loses  million claim over wireless patents” mr desmarais was selected by intellectual property asset management iam magazine as one of the top  individuals companies and institutions that have helped shape the ip market over the past eight years  iammagazine “the players” issue  novemberdecember  iam magazine also selected mr desmarais in its iam  “the world’s leading ip strategists”  mr desmarais and his firm were profiled by the american lawyer media intellectual property magazine in spring  in “back to basics” mr desmarais was selected as the  new york city litigation patent lawyer of the year by the best lawyers in america  th edition mr desmarais was selected by managing intellectual property magazine as us intellectual property practitioner of the year  he was selected by national law journals “winning section” in  in “hand signals work” he was selected by the american lawyer for “ under fortyfive the rising stars of the private bar” he was selected as one of the  best ip trial lawyers in the ip worldwide article “the magnificent seven ips best young trial lawyers” he was also recognized as one of the most successful young litigators in america in the national law journals “ under  a look at some of the most successful young litigators in america” the path towards his career as a kirkland ip litigator was profiled in the ip worldwide article “ip litigation makes desmarais a happy guy” each year since  chambers and partners publishers of the worldfamous guides to law firms and lawyers distinguishes mr desmarais as “the best of the best” for intellectual property in both chambers usa americas leading lawyers for business and chambers global the worlds leading lawyers chambers notes that mr desmarais “enjoys an outstanding reputation as a hardnosed warrior with great legal acumen“ mr desmarais was featured in both young and hungry an article about the american lawyers  ip litigation department of the year and in top guns an article about the american lawyers litigation department of the year for  mr desmarais was featured in “medically devised” an article about theamerica lawyers  ip litigation department of the year additionally mr desmarais was mentioned in “longterm sluggers” also a feature on the american lawyers  ip litigation department of the year mr desmarais was profiled by the journal news on april   in the article “chappaquas desmarais defends trademarks and hightech patents”   boards  committees trustee new york university law school foundation board of trustees  present board member new york university law school center on civil justice 